<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1932-12-22T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1932-12-22T00:00:00-05:00" n="559" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d559">
                            <note rend="inline" type="source">800.51W89 Poland/97</note>
                            <head>
                                <hi rend="italic">Memorandum by the Secretary of State</hi>
                            </head>
                            <opener>
                                <dateline rendition="#right">[<placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi></placeName>,] <date calendar="gregorian" when="1932-12-22">December 22,
                                        1932</date>.</dateline>
                            </opener>
                            <p>The Polish Ambassador brought me the annexed note.<note n="25" xml:id="d559fn25">
                                    <hi rend="italic">Supra.</hi>
                                </note> I told him that the United States Government was not
                                contemplating any immediate initiative in that matter so far as I
                                knew. I explained that if we took any initiative in the immediate
                                future in regard to discussions on the subject of the settlement of
                                any nation’s war debt, it would probably be with those nations
                                which, like Great Britain, had made a distinct sacrifice in meeting
                                the December 15 payment.</p>
                            <closer>
                                <signed>
                                    <persName corresp="#p_SHL1">H[<hi rend="smallcaps">enry</hi>] L.
                                            S[<hi rend="smallcaps">timson</hi>]</persName>
                                </signed>
                            </closer>
                        </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>